lead_paragraph: Derek Fisher had just finished a long playing career when Phil Jackson picked him to coach the New York Knicks. Just 1 1/2 seasons later, Jackson decided he needed someone else.

headline.print_headline: Knicks Fire Coach Derek Fisher; Rambis Gets Interim Job
